abstract: CLEVELAND, Sept. 22.--The mother of the late President is by nature far from demonstrative, and the many distorted utterances of hers which appeared in the newspapers during the campaign, and especially since the assassination, do her great injustice. abstract: So far from seeking a purchaser for the Hawaiian Kingdom, the real object which King KALAKAUA had in view in making a journey around the world was to lay in a new stock of subjects.
